content.title: Function Apps
content.subtitle: My subtitle

inputs.name: partTitle
inputs.value: Query 1

inputs.name: query
inputs.value:
Resources
| where type =~ "microsoft.web/sites"
| where kind contains "functionapp"
| where name startswith "func-"
| extend Environment = extract(@"func-.*-(dev|prod|manualtest|automationtest|uat)$", 1, tolower(name))
| extend Environment = iff(isempty(Environment), "no-env", Environment)
| summarize 
    Count = count(),
    Names = strcat_array(make_list(name), ", ")
    by Environment
| order by Count desc

inputs.name: partTitle
inputs.value: Query 1

inputs.name: query
inputs.value:
Resources
| where type == "microsoft.web/sites"
| where kind contains "functionapp"
| where name contains "dev" or resourceGroup contains "dev"
| project name, location, properties.state

content.subtitle: My subtitle

inputs.name: partTitle
inputs.value: Query 1

inputs.name: query
inputs.value:
Resources
| where type == "microsoft.cdn/profiles"
| where name contains "dev" or resourceGroup contains "dev"
| summarize count() by tostring(properties.resourceState)
| order by count_ desc

chart.title: Avg Origin Health Percentage for afd-rsp-applications-dev-uks where OriginGroup = 'og-rsp-applications-dev-uks', 'og-rsp-applications-dev-uks-cms'
Count Percentage of 5XX for afd-rsp-applications-dev-uks where Endpoint = 'fd-rsp-applications-dev-uks-cveeakgqdgbqexbz.a03.azurefd.net'

inputs.name: partTitle
inputs.value: Query 1

inputs.name: query
inputs.value:
Resources
| where type == "microsoft.cdn/profiles/afdendpoints"
| where name contains "dev" or resourceGroup contains "dev"
| extend origins = properties.origins
| mv-expand origins
| project
    profile = tostring(split(id, "/")[8]),
    endpointName = name,
    endpointHost = tostring(properties.hostName),
    originName = tostring(origins.name),
    originHostName = tostring(origins.properties.hostName),
    enabledState = tostring(origins.properties.enabledState),
    priority = tostring(origins.properties.priority),
    weight = tostring(origins.properties.weight),
    httpPort = tostring(origins.properties.httpPort),
    httpsPort = tostring(origins.properties.httpsPort),
    location,
    resourceGroup
| order by profile, endpointName, originName asc
